    <text type="letter"> 
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.02517.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Blackpool. England<ptr target="loc.02517_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1891-09-19">Sept 19. 91.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Came here yesterday Grand weather, magnificent sunset last night&#8212;such a display
                of gorgeous colour&#8212;golds, silver's
                crimson's, <hi rend="underline">greens,</hi> blues, purples, blacks, greys, browns</p>
            <p>Brilliant moonlight night</p>
            <p>Another grand day this&#8212;write this sitting on beach&#8212;the rising tide
                breaking in curling waves at my feet&#8212;sun shining &#38; shimmering on the
                heaving water. Air most exhilarating &amp; everything bright &amp; beautiful.
                My love to you &amp; to HLT<ptr target="n4267"/> &amp; the rest</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>God bless you</salute>
                <salute>yours affectly</salute>
                <signed rend="center">J Johnston</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.02517.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body> 
